I always LOVE these Gmail posts. Because time after time, I get told that "no Gmail addresses ever duplicate" yet, I have no less than 5 women who share my Gmail account for some reason. They all have their names as firstlast@gmail.com, and mine was a beta name with a period in betweeen (which we all know means nothing) but due to this I get so much stuff it's incredible. I have spoken with an FBI agent after someone interviewed with them. I have explianed to a young woman's mother why I thought she might want to tell her daughter to stop taking nude pictures of herself and leaving herself notes on which guy gets which pics. I have spoken to the Grand Canyon Online University and explained that I do not in fact teach at their school and that their repeated attempts to coerce me due to my prior teaching assignments with them is falling on deaf ears. I have dealt with numerous family reunions that I faield to show up for "even though we reminded you weekly". I have talked to medical bill collectors, credit collectors, a sex linme that claims I defaulted them somehow, and a bakery who I failed to pay at my wedding to a guy named Cyrus (last name is my name).It's just nutty how bad it is. I even call the people direct when I get phone numbers from their confirmation of flights or reservations somewhere and they just tell me I'm wrong and I say okay and let it go. Ignorance may be bliss but I wnder how one could miss so many things like that and either be that stupid.... or they are getting some emails somehow.
